<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_384_r1l26"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vvie Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_384_r1l27">das an ewr vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>e</expan> güt frewnde <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>Stet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> braht habt / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_384_r1l28"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brıef vvol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>vveiſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> wıſſen </ab>
