<ab facs="#facs_384_r1l30">wir <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>güt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnden den 
<del rend="strikethrough"> S </del> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Stet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ew in den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_384_r1l31">vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſachen gedıenen <expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd lıebs vnd <expan>frewntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_384_r1l32">cʒü beweıſen weſten / Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit vvıllen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> </ab>
