<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        wie ir das an ewr und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan> güt frewnde
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>stet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> braht
                        habt, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief
                        wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> wissen, daz uns noch kein antwurt darumb
                                <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist. Dann was wir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>güt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnden den <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>stet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und ew in den und
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sachen gedienen
                            <expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und liebs und
                                <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> czü beweisen westen, das
                                <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
                        mit willen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ut s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
